  "detailed_description": "You are stuck in an apartment building with endless floors.<br>Observe your surroundings carefully to reach the 15th floor and reach the roof of the apartment building.<br><br>Don't overlook any anomalies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834370/extras/0e6c7b35c2801c38a585c51bfa81e072.poster.avif?t=1748534266\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834370/extras/0e6c7b35c2801c38a585c51bfa81e072.webm?t=1748534266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834370/extras/0e6c7b35c2801c38a585c51bfa81e072.mp4?t=1748534266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will encounter different endings depending on your level of understanding of the anomalies you will encounter on the floors.<br><br>If you find anomalies, turn back immediately. Go downstairs.<br><br>If you don't find anomalies, don't turn back. Go upstairs.<br><br>When you reach the 15th floor, 3 different doors await you. You will face different endings at these doors. <br>If you are more careful and make fewer mistakes, you will get the best surprise ending.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834370/extras/ef93c95a0bc789245e28ed2ea20ef833.poster.avif?t=1748534266\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834370/extras/ef93c95a0bc789245e28ed2ea20ef833.webm?t=1748534266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834370/extras/ef93c95a0bc789245e28ed2ea20ef833.mp4?t=1748534266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Play Time</strong><br>20-90 minutes",
